# Atomic Design Refactoring - Walkthrough

## Overview
We have successfully refactored the `conciliacion.app` frontend to follow the Atomic Design methodology. This structure promotes component reusability, consistency, and scalability.

## Changes Implemented

### 1. Directory Structure
Refructured `src/components` into clear layers:
- **Atoms**: [Button](file:///f:/1.%20Cloud/4.%20AI/1.%20Antigravity/ConciliacionWeb/frontend/src/components/atoms/Button.tsx#10-52), [Input](file:///f:/1.%20Cloud/4.%20AI/1.%20Antigravity/ConciliacionWeb/frontend/src/components/atoms/Input.tsx#3-8), [Select](file:///f:/1.%20Cloud/4.%20AI/1.%20Antigravity/ConciliacionWeb/frontend/src/components/atoms/Select.tsx#3-9), [Checkbox](file:///f:/1.%20Cloud/4.%20AI/1.%20Antigravity/ConciliacionWeb/frontend/src/components/atoms/Checkbox.tsx#3-7), [Badge](file:///f:/1.%20Cloud/4.%20AI/1.%20Antigravity/ConciliacionWeb/frontend/src/components/atoms/Badge.tsx#10-36), [Card](file:///f:/1.%20Cloud/4.%20AI/1.%20Antigravity/ConciliacionWeb/frontend/src/components/atoms/Card.tsx#9-18).
- **Molecules**: [Modal](file:///f:/1.%20Cloud/4.%20AI/1.%20Antigravity/ConciliacionWeb/frontend/src/components/molecules/Modal.tsx#41-162) (wrapper), [DataTable](file:///f:/1.%20Cloud/4.%20AI/1.%20Antigravity/ConciliacionWeb/frontend/src/components/molecules/DataTable.tsx#65-276), [ComboBox](file:///f:/1.%20Cloud/4.%20AI/1.%20Antigravity/ConciliacionWeb/frontend/src/components/molecules/ComboBox.tsx#21-216), `FormField` components.
- **Organisms**: `Sidebar`, `FilterBar`, and specific domain components like `Tables/` and `Modals/`.
- **Templates**: [MainLayout](file:///f:/1.%20Cloud/4.%20AI/1.%20Antigravity/ConciliacionWeb/frontend/src/components/templates/MainLayout.tsx#9-22).

### 2. Component Standardization
- **Premium Aesthetics**: Refined [Button](file:///f:/1.%20Cloud/4.%20AI/1.%20Antigravity/ConciliacionWeb/frontend/src/components/atoms/Button.tsx#10-52), [Input](file:///f:/1.%20Cloud/4.%20AI/1.%20Antigravity/ConciliacionWeb/frontend/src/components/atoms/Input.tsx#3-8), and [Select](file:///f:/1.%20Cloud/4.%20AI/1.%20Antigravity/ConciliacionWeb/frontend/src/components/atoms/Select.tsx#3-9) with specific design tokens (shadows, transitions, focus rings) to match a premium feel.
- **Centralization**: All Buttons now use the [Button](file:///f:/1.%20Cloud/4.%20AI/1.%20Antigravity/ConciliacionWeb/frontend/src/components/atoms/Button.tsx#10-52) atom (no more hardcoded HTML buttons). [DataTable](file:///f:/1.%20Cloud/4.%20AI/1.%20Antigravity/ConciliacionWeb/frontend/src/components/molecules/DataTable.tsx#65-276) uses [Button](file:///f:/1.%20Cloud/4.%20AI/1.%20Antigravity/ConciliacionWeb/frontend/src/components/atoms/Button.tsx#10-52) for actions. Modals use standardized [Button](file:///f:/1.%20Cloud/4.%20AI/1.%20Antigravity/ConciliacionWeb/frontend/src/components/atoms/Button.tsx#10-52) and [Card](file:///f:/1.%20Cloud/4.%20AI/1.%20Antigravity/ConciliacionWeb/frontend/src/components/atoms/Card.tsx#9-18) styles.

### 3. Layout Integration
- Created [MainLayout](file:///f:/1.%20Cloud/4.%20AI/1.%20Antigravity/ConciliacionWeb/frontend/src/components/templates/MainLayout.tsx#9-22) template to handle the Sidebar and Page Content structure.
- Refactored [App.tsx](file:///f:/1.%20Cloud/4.%20AI/1.%20Antigravity/ConciliacionWeb/frontend/src/App.tsx) to be cleaner and use the Template.

## Verification
- **Build**: The strict TypeScript build passes, confirming all imports and types are resolved.
- **Visuals**: Components now share a unified design language defined in the Atoms.

## Next Steps
- Continue using the new atoms for any future UI development.
- Refactor the few remaining legacy components in specific pages if any are discovered.
